      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/147/5636",
      "text": [
        " اَلْجَدِّ مَعَ إِخْوَةٍ لِأُمٍّ قَالَ \"إِنَّ فِي كِتَابِ عَلِيٍّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ \"أَنَّ اَلْإِخْوَةَ مِنَ اَلْأُمِّ يَرِثُونَ مَعَ اَلْجَدِّ اَلثُّلُثَ\" \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5636 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Khalid ibn Jarir from Abu Al-Rabi from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding the grandfather inheriting alongside maternal siblings.\nImam (as) said: \"Indeed, in the Book of Ali (as), it is written that 'the maternal siblings inherit one-third along with the grandfather.'\""
        ]
      }
    },
